d107 1
a107 21
KENDA

Small of stature, but quicker than humanly possible,
Kenda tend to be thought of as pests. For those Kenda
able to supress their urges toward flightiness, life
has become very lucrative. 

Rightfully so, they are frequently suspected of being
at the centre of most daring crimes. Their thieving 
abilities are instinctive, and are - even at their worst,
a step above others.

Their slight built and sneaky nature also means that 
people rarely notice them going around on their own
business. Much to their chargrin.


Special Abilities
-------------------
Permanant Sneak
Thief skill bonus
