ORC ORCS
d128 1
a128 13
Strangely enticing, Orcs are medium sized green
creatures endowed with strange abilities. Their
goals in life are unknown to others, but it is
suspected that they work in tandem, controlled
by a secret underground cult.

Although average in most ways, almost in a mimic
of human attributes, they have the uncanny ability
to charm fellow demi-humans into joining their cause.

Completely inexplicably, previously aggressive 
creatures will turn to follow an Orc of great charisma
even unto death. 
